{"id": "1429350746792529921", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "yeah, the entire concept behind exalts from a lore perspective is that awakeners go mad the longer they go unlinked/further away they are from the black pool", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:09:34.088000+00:00"}
{"id": "1429350847271272478", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "and what a link does is it allows a linker to establish a channel with an awakener that allows them to channel that insanity", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:09:58.044000+00:00"}
{"id": "1429350893936967750", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "it builds up until they can release it in a single extreme burst of power to achieve something", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:10:09.170000+00:00"}
{"id": "1429350903701573693", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "content": "the best word of all available would be accumulate but accrue is shorter", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:10:11.498000+00:00"}
{"id": "1429350951038484520", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "that's why the more accurate chinese term for exalt is actually frenzy/madness (and why MTL had that as a term at some points)", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:10:22.784000+00:00"}
{"id": "1429350960584589403", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "content": "accrue sounds cooler than gather", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:10:25.060000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:10:33.248000+00:00"}
{"id": "1429351058433642626", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "but yeah tl;dr from a lore perspective is that the longer the battle goes on, the more and more insane they grow", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T06:10:48.389000+00:00"}
